page.title: 10Aberystwyth car survey(cont)
page.content:
came from Scotland.EJ was the most popular registration as it comes from the Bangor area.Most cars were registered in 1981_82 as 'X'.
Colours. The most popular colours are Red and Blue.We think this is so because people like bright colours.Gold and Silver are less popular because they are metallic colours and are more expensive.Black was surprisingly unpopular because we thought it was coming back into fashion.There were no Pink cars seen.There were only one Peach and one Grey.We saw six Beige cars going into town from Llabadarn. Yellow was quite popular and so was Brown.
